---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    background: "#ffffff"
    fontFamily: "Arial"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Test as Remedy E2E test
    participant Repro as Event-handler regression
    participant API as Karmada API
    participant Cache as Manager informer cache
    participant Handler as Cluster update handler
    participant Queue as Remedy work queue
    participant RC as Remedy controller

    Note over Test,RC: Test timestamps use the runner clock, controller timestamps use the kind-node clock.<br/>Use per-source order and API observations, not sub-second cross-clock ordering.

    rect rgb(254, 242, 242)
    Note over Test,RC: Observed failure on PR #7697 attempt 1
    Test->>API: Create Remedy at 08:34:55.435
    Test->>API: Set DNS condition False at 08:34:55.444
    API-)Cache: Remedy and Cluster watch events
    Cache-)Queue: Enqueue member1

    Queue-)RC: Reconcile at 08:34:55.448
    RC->>Cache: Read a not-yet-aligned Remedy/Cluster view
    RC-->>Queue: Desired actions are empty

    Queue-)RC: Reconcile at 08:34:55.492
    RC->>Cache: Read Remedy plus False condition
    RC->>API: Update remedyActions to TrafficControl
    API-->>Test: Direct GET observes TrafficControl

    Test->>API: Delete Remedy at 08:34:55.519
    API-)Cache: Remedy delete event
    Cache-)Queue: Enqueue member1
    Queue-)RC: Reconcile at 08:34:55.576
    RC->>Cache: Remedy is gone, cached actions are still empty
    Note over RC,Cache: UpdateStatus compares desired empty actions<br/>with the stale cached empty actions.
    RC--xAPI: Skip Status.Update as a DeepEqual no-op
    RC-->>Queue: Log success with empty actions

    API-)Cache: Earlier TrafficControl status becomes visible
    Cache-)Handler: Cluster update with unchanged Conditions<br/>and RemedyActions empty to TrafficControl
    Handler->>Handler: Compare Conditions only
    Handler--xQueue: RemedyActions-only update is not enqueued

    loop Direct API polling for 420 seconds
        Test->>API: GET Cluster member1
        API-->>Test: remedyActions still contains TrafficControl
    end

    Note over Cache,RC: No periodic requeue and no later Remedy reconcile.<br/>The stale action cannot converge in this lifecycle.
    end

    rect rgb(255, 247, 237)
    Note over Repro,Queue: Deterministic regression replays the same dropped recovery edge
    Repro->>Handler: old/new Conditions equal<br/>RemedyActions empty to TrafficControl
    Handler--xQueue: Current code leaves queue length 0
    Queue-->>Repro: Assertion fails: got 0, want 1
    end

    rect rgb(240, 253, 244)
    Note over API,RC: Fixed invariant: ignore an update only when both Conditions and RemedyActions are unchanged
    API-)Cache: TrafficControl status becomes visible
    Cache-)Handler: Same Conditions and changed RemedyActions
    Handler-)Queue: Enqueue member1
    Queue-)RC: Compensation reconcile
    RC->>Cache: Read TrafficControl and no matching Remedy
    RC->>API: Update remedyActions to empty
    API-)Cache: Empty remedyActions becomes visible
    Cache-)Handler: RemedyActions changed again
    Handler-)Queue: Enqueue one final reconciliation
    Queue-)RC: Reconcile current empty state
    RC--xAPI: Skip equal Status.Update
    Note over Queue,RC: No new API write means no further Cluster update event.<br/>The compensation terminates without periodic requeue.
    end
